> 
> Another way can be to get the metadata along with the `GET` API on tables?

So Subbu's suggestion for GET api on tables will be something like:
```
{
  "OFFLINE" : {
  ...
  },
  "REALTIME" : {
  ...
  },
  "METADATA" : {
    "REALTIME" : {
      "creationTime" : "20201206T2130Z"
    },
    "OFFLINE" : {
      "creationTime" : "20201206T2130Z"
    }
  }
}
```

