I like sending out metadata along with the table API. What do you say, @kishoreg ? This also allows us to add other metadata later on if needed.

I am not sure I prefer including  metadata in the table config znode

If we are modeling it as a separate call, let us not have one for creatoinTime alone. 

Let us call it `/tables/{tableName}/metadata` or `/tables/{tableName}/info`
@kishoreg  any preferences here?

